title: 11/04/20 HOUR 2- Chris Collinsworth

description:
Chris Collinsworth tells Dan that he used to love election night because it was one night. Chris says now the elections have become too drawn out. Chris tells Dan that the Tampa Bay Buccaneers now look like Tom Brady in New England with weapons.
